{"tid":1087781,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"Macau fan覆核——整個商界已經騰雞到恐襲式崩潰！","createTime":"2019-04-01T14:33:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-01T14:42:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e89b3b5b063486941a181a34fb822f4abd043755","tid":1087781,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T14:33:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/19512/%E5%8A%89%E9%91%BE%E9%9B%84-%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-19512/macau-fan%E8%A6%86%E6%A0%B8%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E6%95%B4%E5%80%8B%E5%95%86%E7%95%8C%E5%B7%B2%E7%B6%93%E9%A8%B0%E9%9B%9E%E5%88%B0%E6%81%90%E8%A5%B2%E5%BC%8F%E5%B4%A9%E6%BD%B0%EF%BC%81\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F19512%2F%25E5%258A%2589%25E9%2591%25BE%25E9%259B%2584-%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-19512%2Fmacau-fan%25E8%25A6%2586%25E6%25A0%25B8%25E2%2580%2594%25E2%2580%2594%25E6%2595%25B4%25E5%2580%258B%25E5%2595%2586%25E7%2595%258C%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E7%25B6%2593%25E9%25A8%25B0%25E9%259B%259E%25E5%2588%25B0%25E6%2581%2590%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E5%25BC%258F%25E5%25B4%25A9%25E6%25BD%25B0%25EF%25BC%2581&d=kym%2Bu5moN5dZdxbwy4XQi0YnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=142cde14\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/19512/%E5%8A%89%E9%91%BE%E9%9B%84-%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-19512/macau-fan%E8%A6%86%E6%A0%B8%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E6%95%B4%E5%80%8B%E5%95%86%E7%95%8C%E5%B7%B2%E7%B6%93%E9%A8%B0%E9%9B%9E%E5%88%B0%E6%81%90%E8%A5%B2%E5%BC%8F%E5%B4%A9%E6%BD%B0%EF%BC%81</a><br />\n<br />\nMacau fan覆核&mdash;&mdash;整個商界已經騰雞到恐襲式崩潰！<br />\n撰文: 一悠 | 發佈日期: 01.04.19<br />\n<br />\n請支持《眾新聞》，成為訂戶<br />\n<br />\n真正是Macau fan 啦！風扇劉澳門衰咗，宣佈要申請司法覆核，主要是，修例不可有追訴權 ，很明顯是想為他自己度身訂做，為求不上身。但根本修例都未開始，Macau fan就申請司法覆核，很大機會不批准。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2019/04/%E5%8A%89%E9%91%BE%E9%9B%84-%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-20190401211212_3a0f_large.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2019%2F04%2F%25E5%258A%2589%25E9%2591%25BE%25E9%259B%2584-%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-20190401211212_3a0f_large.jpg&h=1a0d410c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劉鑾雄委託律師向高院申請司法覆核政府提出修訂逃犯條例。《蘋果日報》資料照片<br />\n整個商界，已經陷入騰雞到恐襲式崩潰的狀態。<br />\n<br />\n這次林鄭就是掟石入公廁 &mdash;&mdash;激起公糞&mdash;&mdash;公憤，什麼污糟邋遢嘢全部反彈曬出嚟！<br />\n<br />\n三隧分流，有人反對就可以撤回，這次送中修例，更多人反對，12000人遊行，林鄭卻剛剛還是咬牙切齒地說&mdash;&mdash;絕不撤案，愈強硬愈顯得有嘢，另有目的。<br />\n<br />\n台灣不是有死刑嗎， 把那個疑匪戒過去，分分鐘槍斃，這豈不是違反了&mdash;&mdash; 不能移交去有死刑的地方的概念嗎？卻好像沒有什麼人提過這點。那個疑犯，近日肯定也騰雞到崩潰一族。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥更顯得這件事有古惑，有命令在背後，各位有何高見？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請加入成為眾新聞的月費訂戶，長期支持我們的工作。所有訂戶都可以收到我們的「每周時事」通訊 。<br />\n<br />\n月費訂戶網址：<a href=\"http://hkcnews.com/aboutus/#subscribe\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkcnews.com%2Faboutus%2F%23subscribe&d=kym%2Bu5moN5dZdxbwy4XQi0YnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=9950e4cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">hkcnews.com/aboutus/#subscribe</a><br />\n<br />\n博客 | 一悠<br />\n【一悠・到此一遊】喜歡談古論今，也常談股論金。心理、鋼琴、股票、教育，交义感染，交流一下。學歷：香港中文大學文學士，研究院教育文憑，澳洲新南威爾斯大學碩士（堅有證書㗎，卻無野雞大學博士，也不必請律師去找證書）"},{"pid":"236924806ec6de1633343e15acec6cb2ce0ebd9a","tid":1087781,"uid":15880,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T14:42:49.000Z","msg":"特首係王志民, 關林鄭洋事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}